Jika bagian tubuh tidak digunakan,
itu dianggap tak perlu.

218
00:14:22,486 --> 00:14:26,031 
Orang yang tak memiliki sendi
disebut evolusi yang baru.

219
00:14:27,116 --> 00:14:29,493 
Seperti yang kau lihat di rontgen ini,

220
00:14:29,618 --> 00:14:32,496 
Izuku punya dua sendi.

221
00:14:34,081 --> 00:14:38,627 
Itu langka dalam generasinya,
dia tipe yang tak mempunyai Bakat.

222
00:14:46,468 --> 00:14:49,388 
<i>Kau lihat itu?</i>
<i>Dia sudah menyelamatkan 100 orang.</i>

223
00:14:50,014 --> 00:14:52,725 
<i>Bahkan belum 10 menit.</i>

224
00:14:52,808 --> 00:14:53,893 
<i>Itu gila.</i>

225
00:14:55,185 --> 00:14:56,604 
<i>Lihat, dia tertawa.</i>

226
00:14:57,771 --> 00:14:58,981 
<i>Sudah tidak apa-apa.</i>

227
00:14:59,189 --> 00:15:01,942 
<i>Kenapa? Karena aku sudah di sini!</i>

228
00:15:04,361 --> 00:15:05,529 
<i>Bu,</i>

229
00:15:07,615 --> 00:15:11,285 
<i>dia membantu semua orang dengan senyuman.</i>

230
00:15:14,079 --> 00:15:16,415 
<i>Dia Pahlawan yang hebat.</i>

231
00:15:25,507 --> 00:15:28,677 
Bisakah aku menjadi seperti dia?

232
00:15:34,934 --> 00:15:36,268 
Maafkan ibu, Izuku!

233
00:15:37,019 --> 00:15:38,646 
Ibu sungguh minta maaf...

234
00:15:43,484 --> 00:15:44,652 
<i>Bukan begitu.</i>

235
00:15:44,902 --> 00:15:46,111 
<i>Bukan itu, Bu.</i>

236
00:15:47,738 --> 00:15:48,864 
<i>Di saat itu</i>

237
00:15:49,198 --> 00:15:50,824 
<i>aku ingin kau mengatakan...</i>

238
00:15:53,619 --> 00:15:56,956 
PERHATIKAN KEPALA ANDA

239
00:15:58,582 --> 00:16:00,084 
Aku berjanji di hari itu.

240
00:16:01,210 --> 00:16:03,963 
Benar, jangan pedulikan kata orang.

241
00:16:04,713 --> 00:16:06,423 
Angkat kepala dan terus maju.

242
00:16:21,730 --> 00:16:22,648 
Penjahat!

243
00:16:24,650 --> 00:16:27,319 
Ini jubah tak terlihat ukuran menengah.

244
00:16:34,535 --> 00:16:35,744 
Tidak apa-apa.

245
00:16:35,995 --> 00:16:38,038 
Aku hanya mengambil alih tubuhmu.

246
00:16:38,163 --> 00:16:39,331 
Tenanglah.

247
00:16:39,456 --> 00:16:42,334 
Sakitnya hanya selama 45 detik.

248
00:16:42,459 --> 00:16:44,461 
Kau akan merasa lega.

249
00:16:45,879 --> 00:16:47,965 
Aku tak bisa bernapas…

250
00:16:48,674 --> 00:16:52,344 
Bagaimana caramu menarikku?
Aku ini cairan.

251
00:16:52,970 --> 00:16:56,515 
Terima kasih atas segalanya,
kau adalah pahlawanku.

252
00:16:57,307 --> 00:17:01,937 
Aku tak menyangka akan sampai ke kota ini.

253
00:17:03,605 --> 00:17:06,483 
<i>Tubuhku... mati rasa...</i>

254
00:17:07,776 --> 00:17:09,945 
<i>Aku akan mati.</i>

255
00:17:10,904 --> 00:17:12,156 
<i>Apa aku akan mati?</i>

256
00:17:15,576 --> 00:17:16,660 
<i>Aku sekarat…</i>

257
00:17:17,536 --> 00:17:18,704 
<i>Seseorang…</i>

258
00:17:20,122 --> 00:17:21,165 
<i>Seseorang…</i>

259
00:17:22,332 --> 00:17:23,417 
<i>Tidak!</i>

260
00:17:28,964 --> 00:17:31,341 
Semuanya akan baik-baik saja, Anak Muda.

261
00:17:37,848 --> 00:17:39,516 
Aku di sini!

262
00:17:49,610 --> 00:17:53,906 
<i>Texas Smash!</i>

263
00:18:01,538 --> 00:18:03,165 
Tekanan angin!

264
00:18:20,766 --> 00:18:21,975 
<i>All Might...</i>

265
00:18:32,653 --> 00:18:34,321 
Syukurlah.

266
00:18:38,242 --> 00:18:39,993 
Aku lega kau baik-baik saja.

267
00:18:40,452 --> 00:18:42,079 
Aku minta maaf,

268
00:18:42,371 --> 00:18:44,706 
pertarungan tadi melibatkanmu.

269
00:18:45,165 --> 00:18:47,876 
Biasanya aku tak membuat kesalahan
seperti ini,

270
00:18:47,960 --> 00:18:50,337 
tapi aku sedang tak bertugas
dan berada di area baru.

271
00:18:50,420 --> 00:18:51,839 
Aku terlalu bersemangat.

272
00:18:55,300 --> 00:18:58,220 
Tapi, ini berkat bantuanmu, terima kasih.

273
00:18:59,012 --> 00:19:00,722 
Aku menangkapnya dengan aman.

274
00:19:03,892 --> 00:19:07,229 
<i>Pahlawan nomor satu, All Might...</i>

275
00:19:07,354 --> 00:19:09,606 
<i>Itu sungguh dia.</i>

276
00:19:09,731 --> 00:19:11,024 
<i>Tak seperti aslinya</i>

277
00:19:11,775 --> 00:19:13,944 
<i>saat kau melihatnya secara langsung!</i>

278
00:19:16,113 --> 00:19:17,656 
Oh, tanda tangan...

279
00:19:17,781 --> 00:19:19,533 
Tanda tangan...

280
00:19:19,825 --> 00:19:20,909 
Di buku catatanku!

281
00:19:22,202 --> 00:19:23,620 
Sudah ada.

282
00:19:24,955 --> 00:19:26,623 
Terima kasih!

283
00:19:26,748 --> 00:19:29,543 
Aku akan menyimpannya
sebagai harta selamanya.

284
00:19:29,626 --> 00:19:30,544 
Baik!

285
00:19:31,211 --> 00:19:34,298 
Aku akan mengantarkan ini ke polisi.

286
00:19:35,048 --> 00:19:36,967 
Kita bertemu lagi di layar TV.

287
00:19:38,719 --> 00:19:40,512 
Apa? Sudah?

288
00:19:40,637 --> 00:19:43,932 
Pro selalu bertarung melawan musuh
dan waktu.

289
00:19:45,475 --> 00:19:49,521 
<i>Tapi masih ada yang harus aku tanya.</i>

290
00:19:51,565 --> 00:19:53,567 
Tolong dukung aku,

291
00:19:54,735 --> 00:19:58,739 
aku mengandalkanmu.

292
00:20:04,995 --> 00:20:07,331 
Lepaskan! Kau terlalu berlebihan!

293
00:20:07,581 --> 00:20:11,168 
Jika kulepaskan, aku akan mati!

294
00:20:12,002 --> 00:20:12,878 
Kau benar.

295
00:20:13,212 --> 00:20:15,380 
Aku punya...

296
00:20:15,505 --> 00:20:18,050 
Banyak hal...

297
00:20:18,133 --> 00:20:19,635 
yang ingin kutanyakan...

298
00:20:20,219 --> 00:20:21,428 
Baiklah.

299
00:20:21,678 --> 00:20:23,639 
Sekarang, tutup mulut dan matamu.

300
00:20:36,276 --> 00:20:37,527 
Sial...

301
00:20:44,326 --> 00:20:46,245 
STASIUN CABANG IKOU

302
00:20:50,123 --> 00:20:51,833 
Itu sangat mengerikan.

303
00:20:52,584 --> 00:20:53,710 
Ya ampun,

304
00:20:54,294 --> 00:20:56,838 
minta orang-orang di bawah
untuk menolongmu.

305
00:20:57,130 --> 00:20:59,132 
Aku tak ada waktu.

306
00:20:59,258 --> 00:21:00,592 
Jadi sampai sini saja.

307
00:21:01,093 --> 00:21:02,594 
Hei, tunggu.

308
00:21:02,886 --> 00:21:04,304 
Tidak mau.

309
00:21:05,013 --> 00:21:07,474 
- Tapi...
<i>-</i> <i>Urungkan niatmu.</i>

310
00:21:10,769 --> 00:21:14,815 
<i>Maafkan aku Izuku, maafkan aku...</i>

311
00:21:15,232 --> 00:21:17,609 
<i>Memangnya kau bisa apa?</i>

312
00:21:17,776 --> 00:21:19,695 
Kau tidak punya Bakat!

313
00:21:25,575 --> 00:21:28,287 
<i>Mungkin itu benar</i>

314
00:21:31,039 --> 00:21:33,417 
tapi tetap saja

315
00:21:34,960 --> 00:21:35,961 
aku...

316
00:21:43,802 --> 00:21:46,263 
Bisakah aku menjadi Pahlawan
meskipun tak punya Bakat?

317
00:21:49,850 --> 00:21:51,685 
Bisakah seseorang tanpa Bakat

318
00:21:52,853 --> 00:21:54,896 
