319
00:22:07,075 --> 00:22:08,493 
<i>Bertemu dengan All Might</i>

320
00:22:09,077 --> 00:22:10,203 
<i>adalah keajaiban.</i>

321
00:22:11,121 --> 00:22:13,957 
<i>Saat ini, aku masih tak tahu</i>

322
00:22:15,417 --> 00:22:19,671 
<i>seberapa besar itu akan mengubah takdirku.</i>

323
00:22:23,675 --> 00:22:28,764
{\an8}<i>Di dunia yang mengelilingiku</i>
<i>Dan sisi kelamku</i>

324
00:22:28,889 --> 00:22:33,435
{\an8}<i>Meski kubayangkan, kuraih,</i>
<i>Tetap terasa jauh</i>

325
00:22:38,940 --> 00:22:42,402
{\an8}<i>Saat terasa mendekat</i>

326
00:22:42,527 --> 00:22:47,491
{\an8}<i>Aku terbangun dari mimpi</i>
<i>dan tetap terasa jauh</i>

327
00:22:48,492 --> 00:22:54,498
{\an8}<i>Kota dipenuhi pertanda fajar</i>

328
00:22:54,581 --> 00:22:56,917
{\an8}<i>Menyembunyikan suara</i>

329
00:22:57,584 --> 00:22:59,961
{\an8}<i>Dalam keraguan, aku mencari</i>

330
00:23:00,045 --> 00:23:06,802
{\an8}<i>Makna keberadaanku</i>

331
00:23:07,344 --> 00:23:12,641
{\an8}<i>Di dunia yang mengelilingiku</i>
Dan masa kelamku

332
00:23:12,766 --> 00:23:16,853
{\an8}<i>Meski kubayangkan, kuraih,</i>
<i>Tetap terasa jauh</i>

333
00:23:16,978 --> 00:23:22,359
{\an8}<i>Apa yang harus aku singkirkan</i>
<i>Untuk menggapainya?</i>

334
00:23:22,484 --> 00:23:27,114
{\an8}<i>Tak peduli berapa kali</i>
<i>aku berteriak kencang</i>

335
00:23:27,197 --> 00:23:31,368
{\an8}<i>Pada akhirnya, aku hanya diriku sendiri</i>

336
00:23:31,493 --> 00:23:36,873
{\an8}<i>Tak peduli apakah ini mimpi atau kenyataan</i>

337
00:23:36,998 --> 00:23:41,294
{\an8}<i>Aku yakin bisa melampaui</i>

338
00:23:41,753 --> 00:23:44,256
{\an8}<i>Tak apa-apa jika terjatuh</i>

339
00:23:44,339 --> 00:23:46,174
{\an8}<i>Menangislah</i>

340
00:23:46,258 --> 00:23:48,552
{\an8}<i>Suatu hari semuanya</i>

341
00:23:48,677 --> 00:23:51,096
{\an8}<i>Akan mekar menjadi bunga</i>

